name: Omicron (COMPUTE!)
overview: A shoot'em up published in COMPUTE!'s Gazette 1987/04 (Issue #46), COMPUTE!'s Gazette 1988 Special Issue. Be ready and alert. A host of deadly enemies can make quick work of you in this frantically paced, multilevel arcade-action game for the 64. A joystick is required. "Omicron" is a game which creates a universe full of hostile aliens. To play and win, you must survive 16 waves of 15 enemies each. This is anything but an easy task — you'll be facing some of the deadliest and fastest creatures ever to visit the screen of your computer,
